description: Magle Chemoswed Holding AB engages in the provision of contract development and manufacturing services to the pharmaceutical and medical device industry. The company is headquartered in Malmo, Skane. The company went IPO on 2020-06-30. The firm is located in Malmo, Sweden. The company provides development and manufacturing services to healthcare companies as well as innovating and supplying new products based on the Company proprietary technology platform.
name: Magle Chemoswed Holding AB
